de>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Element&nbsp;<strong><code>&lt;section&gt;</code>&nbsp;</strong>stanowi samodzielną sekcję&nbsp;tworzącą dokument HTML, której nie można przedstawić za pomocą bardziej szczegółowej semantycznie sekcji. Element &lt;section&gt; zazwyczaj posiada nagłówek.</p>\n\n<p>Przykładowo, część&nbsp;nawigacyjna powinna być objęta&nbsp;elementem <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, ale lista wyników wyszukiwania albo wyświetlana mapa i jej sterowanie nie&nbsp;mają dla siebie szczegółowego elementu, więc powinny zostać umieszczone w&nbsp;<code>&lt;section&gt;</code>.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Content categories</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Flow content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#sectioning_content\">Sectioning content</a>, palpable content.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Permitted content</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Flow content</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag omission</th>\n   <td>None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Permitted parents</th>\n   <td>Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">flow content</a>. Note that a <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> element must not be a descendant of an <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a> element.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Permitted ARIA roles</th>\n   <td><code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#alert\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">alert</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#alertdialog\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">alertdialog</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#application\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">application</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#banner\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">banner</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#complementary\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">complementary</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#contentinfo\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">contentinfo</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#dialog\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">dialog</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#document\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">document</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#feed\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">feed</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#log\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">log</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#main\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">main</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#marquee\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">marquee</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#navigation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">navigation</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#search\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">search</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#status\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">status</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#tabpanel\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">tabpanel</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM interface</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atrybuty","title":"Atrybuty","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Element zawiera tylko&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">global attributes</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"użycie","title":"Użycie","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Każdy&nbsp;element&nbsp;<code>&lt;section&gt;</code>&nbsp;powinien zazwyczaj zawierać nagłówek&nbsp;(<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>) jako element potomny&nbsp;<code>&lt;section&gt;</code>.</li>\n <li>Jeśli jest konieczne oddzielić podgrupy w treści elementu&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>,&nbsp;&nbsp;używa się elementów<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n <li>Nie używa się elementu <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> w celu stworzenia ogólnego kontenera; do tego służy&nbsp;element <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>, szczególnie nie robi się tego jesli ma to służyć tylko do nadania stylów.&nbsp;Praktyczną zasadą jest to, że wsytąpeinie elementu &lt;section&gt; powinną&nbsp;być logiczne&nbsp;w schemacie dokumentu.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład_1","title":"Przykład 1","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wcześniej","title":"Wcześniej","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Bunch of awesome content<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"teraz","title":"Teraz","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Bunch of awesome content<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład_2","title":"Przykład 2","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wcześniej_2","title":"Wcześniej","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bird.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bird<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\