ailable in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Sections and outlines of an HTML5 document</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Atrybuty","id":"atrybuty"},{"text":"Użycie","id":"użycie"},{"text":"Przykład 1","id":"przykład